Usage: summaryReport [-help] [-outdir <string>] [-noText  | -noHtml ] [-outfile <string> | -noText ] [-noHtml  | -browser ] [-exclude_base_cell_for_density <libCell/ptnCell>+ | -exclude_inst_prefix <string>]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-browser                        # display results in browser (bool, optional)
-exclude_base_cell_for_density <libCell/ptnCell>+
                                # specifies the list of cells to be exclude
                                # from density report
                                # ((libCell/ptnCell)+, optional)
-exclude_inst_prefix <string>   # specifies the list of prefixes to map all
                                # instance names to be exclude from density
                                # report (string, optional)
-noHtml                         # not in html format (bool, optional)
-noText                         # not in text format (bool, optional)
-outdir <string>                # out dir name (string, optional)
-outfile <string>               # out file name (string, optional)